@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_exybfd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.72 * 0.07)
    v2 = wp.cos((0.09 / (v0 + 0.09 + v0 + 0.72)))
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.32) - (v2 + 0.13 / v0 + 0.68)) + ((v2 + 0.54 - v2 + 0.97) * tmp))
    v0 = wp.abs((0.13 * (v2 + 0.39 / tmp + 0.16)))
    data[tid] = v0
